<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/33001ATHPSRJLTTHKPJHTBJLTTSMCRPQH> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "2026 World Tour Paddling Film Festival";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$23.50 Per Person</span><span><br/></span>Including fees & charges<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Vernon Paddling Centre</span> and <span class=\"BoldText\">Vernon Adaptive </span>once again bring the <span class=\"BoldText\">World Tour Paddling Film Festival</span> to the Vernon area. The Paddling Film Festival has been showcasing the very best paddling films since 2006.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Watch and be inspired to explore rivers, lakes and oceans, push extremes, appreciate wild places and embrace the paddling lifestyle. Join us for this World Tour screening, then go paddling! We’re pretty sure you’ll want to. The Club will have outrigger boats on display and a cash-only concession by Vernon Adaptive, with door prizes during intermission.<span><br/></span>
""";
