<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/60001AQMCNPHJDPMRBPJPHQTSVTJDCRKQ> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Celeigh Cardinal";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$49.00 Per Person</span><span><br/></span>Including fees & charges<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Celeigh Cardinal </span>is a <span class=\"BoldText\">JUNO Award-winning</span> singer-songwriter known for her powerhouse vocals and captivating live performances. Blending soul, folk, and pop, she creates shows that are both emotionally intimate and musically commanding.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Her latest album, Boundless Possibilities (2024), earned critical acclaim and marked a bold evolution in her sound—bringing new depth and energy to her live performances.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>On stage, Celeigh pairs soaring vocals with heartfelt storytelling, drawing audiences into a shared emotional experience. Her natural warmth, playful spirit, and authenticity create an immediate connection, making every show feel personal—whether in a theatre or festival setting.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Having toured across Canada and internationally, she has built a reputation as a must-see performer who doesn’t just sing her songs—she lives them, leaving audiences moved long after the final note.
""";
