<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/5651AKNSDSRGSMPDGTVSBMHJQKPTSJTBJ> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Circus Incognitus";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$18.00 All Seats</span><span><br/></span>Includes Fees & Tax<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Jamie Adkins is a performer in the vaudeville tradition of Charlie Chaplin and Buster Keaton. With no hi-tech distractions, his irresistible character heroically battles with the everyday objects of life, permanently on the verge of disaster… moving but hilarious.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Everywhere he goes, the public, adults and children alike, laugh out loud at the humour and marvel at the multi-talented performance of Jamie in Circus Incognitus. An unforgettable one-man circus comedy!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Recognized worldwide for his undeniable talent as an acrobat, juggler and clown, Jamie Adkins has performed Circus Incognitus over 1,200 times across 27 countries and continues to captivate audiences with his unique blend of skill and humour!
""";
