<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/53601AHTLLGLRDMLTLNLGVRKSBJRRTMLG> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Completely Creedence Band - A Tribute to CCR";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$54.00 Per Person</span><span><br/></span>Including fees & charges<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Completely Creedence is a passionate and authentic tribute to the legendary music of Creedence Clearwater Revival. Known for their high-energy performances and faithful sound, the band brings the timeless hits of CCR to life for audiences of all ages.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Fronted by Jamie Robertson, whose voice and presence capture the unmistakable spirit of John Fogerty, the band delivers a powerful and genuine live experience. Backed by a group of seasoned musicians—Murray Atkinson (lead guitar), Lance Lapointe (bass), and Grant Baird (drums)—Completely Creedence recreates the signature grooves, swampy rhythms, and driving energy that made CCR one of the most iconic bands of all time.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From “Proud Mary” and “Bad Moon Rising” to “Fortunate Son” and “Have You Ever Seen the Rain,” audiences can expect a night filled with unforgettable songs that defined a generation. Their performances are more than just a concert—they’re a celebration of music that continues to resonate decades later. Having performed across theatres, festivals, and community events, Completely Creedence has built a reputation for delivering consistently engaging and crowd-pleasing shows. Whether it’s an intimate theatre setting or a lively outdoor festival, the band connects with audiences through the music we all know and love.<span><br/></span>
""";
