<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/59202ATRBRCGRHHKQJBLJGDPPMVSKKQTP> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Honky Tonk Harmonies!";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$59 - All Seats</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">includes fees & taxes</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>With their unique brand of blood harmony and brotherly banter, <span class=\"BoldText\">THE ZMED BROTHERS</span> (of The Everly Brothers Experience) pay a family style tribute to Americas Golden Age of Country & Western Music in this informative and wildly fun roots review of over 20 seminal classics. From Appalachia to California, <span class=\"BoldText\">Zach and Dylan</span> paint a mid 20th century portrait of music histories most pivotal time through iconic stories and legendary hits by: The Louvin Brothers, Hank Williams, Merle Haggard, Buck Owens, George Jones, Earnest Tubb, Bob Wills, The Delmore Brothers, Hank Locklin, Johnny Cash, Ray Price, Don Gibson, Webb Pierce, Eddie Arnold, Ned Miller, and more! Join <span class=\"BoldText\">The Zmed Brothers & The Bird Dogs Band</span> as they raise a full & heartfelt glass, to celebrate the spirit of Americana with a top shelf blend of Honky Tonk Harmonies.<span><br/></span>
""";
