<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/44401ADDCBDNQTQBKSGKTVMSVMQDMMLLG> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "MENOPAUSE THE MUSICAL";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$59.00 Adults<span><br/></span>$49.00 Members & Seniors<span><br/></span></span><span class=\"BoldText\">$35 Students (Ages 25 & under)</span><span><br/></span>Includes fees & surcharges<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Menopause The Musical® - COME JOIN OUR SISTERHOOD!</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Set in Bloomingdale's department store, four women at a lingerie sale have nothing in common except a black lace bra, but this Canadian All-Star Cast makes fun of their hot flashes, night sweats, mood swings, wrinkles, memory loss, not enough sex, too much sex, chocolate binges, and much, much more!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This high-spirted musical parody, staged to classic tunes from the ‘60s, ‘70s and ‘80s will have you cheering and dancing in the aisles! See what more than 17 million women and fans worldwide have been laughing about for over 20 years!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Bring your Mother, Daughter, Sister and Friends!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Menopause The Musical is hilarious, delightful and highly entertaining… but best of all, it’s empowering!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>“Fresh, funny and simply terrific!” – LA Times<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>It's the Hilarious Celebration of Women and The Change!®<span><br/></span>
""";
