<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/68202ARKSLKHPVVPNTVMMNNJTKBHGJLKQ> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "NOCCA - JoyRide";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$45.00 Adult<span><br/></span></span><span class=\"BoldText\">$25.00 Student</span><span><br/></span>Including fees & charges<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">JoyRide</span> is a dynamic Canadian jazz crossover and classical-klezmer duo featuring musicians <span class=\"BoldText\">Colin Maier</span> (oboe, musical saw, and vocals) and <span class=\"BoldText\">Mark Camilleri</span> (accordion and piano). Together, they bring an energetic, genre-bending performance that seamlessly fuses styles from Latin, klezmer and bebop to folk, ragtime and tango. ​
""";
