<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/5536AKJSKLTRHTRLNKDKQVRPTLPCCJBHB> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "OSO - Beethoven's Fifth";
  schema:description """
	Experience the symphony that changed music forever. Shocking at the time of its premiere with its emotional intensity, today Beethoven’s 5th is one of the world’s most recognizable works of art. After more than a decade, the OSO returns to this iconic masterpiece to close the season with this monument of musical expression. This concert also features the OSO Chorus in Ola Gjeilo’s Sunrise Mass, a profound and expressive journey, full of soaring melodies and walls of sonic power.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Program</span><span><br/></span>Ola Gijielo: Sunrise Mass<span><br/></span>Beethoven: Symphony No. 5, op. 67
""";
