<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/50001ALBDLSVMDTDTMKNPPLMDQMDRBTLK> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Raine Maida & Chantal Kreviazuk";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$89.00 Adult</span><span><br/></span>*Includes fees & tax<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Raine Maida</span> and <span class=\"BoldText\">Chantal Kreviazuk</span> are Canada’s most influential “cultural couples”.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Chantal, made her critically acclaimed full-length debut, Under These Rocks and Stones in 1997. Since, the Winnipeg born singer-songwriter has earned 3 JUNO Awards and a Grammy Award, recording 10 albums, including a live album and a holiday album.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Simultaneously, <span class=\"BoldText\">Raine</span> forged a dynamic solo career in addition to being the front man for the band <span class=\"BoldText\">Our Lady Peace - </span>also a 4-time JUNO Award winner, including “Rock Album of the Year” in 2003 (Gravity) and in 1998 (Clumsy).<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The pair has also co-written hits for artists such as Kelly Clarkson, David Cook and Carrie Underwood; while Chantal herself, has written songs with Drake, Kendrick Lamar & Gwen Stefani.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Kreviazuk and Maida are equally committed to lending their help to those in need. The couple were awarded the Order of Canada for their efforts to raise awareness and support for human and animal rights, mental health, education and the environment.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Their collaborative album, I<span class=\"BoldText\">’m Going to Break Your Heart</span> was released with an accompanying documentary—capturing the couple’s personal struggles and musical journey—all to inspire a generation of a cycle-breaking and hope for a more peaceful future.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">DIAMOND VIP PACKAGE: $249.00 </span>(Maximum 35 people)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><ul><li> Private Pre-Show Reception & soundcheck & Q&A with Raine & Chantal</li><li> Photo opportunity to commemorate your evening with Raine & Chantal</li><li> Signed copy of “I’m Going to Break Your Heart”</li><li> Commemorative VIP gift item</li><li> Exclusive VIP laminate and lanyard</li><li> Privileged early access to Merchandise</li></ul><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">GOLD VIP PACKAGE:</span> $79.00<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><ul><li> Signed copy of “I’m Going to Break Your Heart”</li><li> Commemorative VIP gift item</li><li> Exclusive VIP laminate and lanyard</li></ul><span><br/></span>Buy directly for VIP: <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.raineandchantal.com/tour-vip\">TOUR &amp; VIP — RaineandChantal</a> (<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.raineandchantal.com/tour-vip\">https://www.raineandchantal.com/tour-vip</a>)<span><br/></span>(100% of each VIP package goes to the Artist)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Don’t miss this chance to see Canada’s own Raine Maida & Chantal Kreviazuk for an unforgettable VDPAC Signature Concert Series experience!
""";
