  schema:name "Seussical Jr.";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$15.25 - Admit<span><br/></span>$8 - Children under 12</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">includes fees & taxes</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Perfect for audiences of all ages—don’t miss this Seuss-tastic musical production!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Journey into the whimsical Jungle of Nool, where Horton the Elephant discovers a tiny world on a speck of dust and bravely vows to protect the Whos of Whoville. Guided by the mischievous Cat in the Hat and joined by an unforgettable cast of colorful characters—including Gertrude McFuzz, Mayzie La Bird, and the Wickersham Brothers—this musical reminds us that “a person’s a person, no matter how small.” With catchy songs, lively choreography, and bright costumes, Seussical Jr. delivers laughter, warmth, and meaningful moments from start to finish.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This student-led production showcases the talent, dedication, and passion of local young performers, bringing classic stories to life with fresh energy and enthusiasm. Whether you’re a lifelong Dr. Seuss fan or discovering these characters for the first time, Seussical Jr. promises an entertaining and uplifting night at the theatre.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Bring the whole family, invite your friends, and support local arts while enjoying a Seuss-tacular evening filled with music, laughter, and unforgettable fun. Think big, dream boldly, and join us at Theatre on the Hill for a magical theatrical experience you won’t want to miss!
""";
