<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/45201ARKHJCBNTTPVRDPLBGRLGJLSLDSJ> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Standing Ovation 2026 Show 1";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$39.00 Adult (19-65)<span><br/></span>$34.00 Student/Senior (13-18/65+)<span><br/></span></span><span class=\"BoldText\">$27.00 Youth (5-12)<span><br/></span></span><span class=\"BoldText\">$ 9.00 Toddler</span><span><br/></span>Including fees & charges<span><br/></span><a href=\"https://purchase.ticketseller.ca/ChooseSeats/45201\">BUY June 5 at 6:30 pm</a><span><br/></span><a href=\"https://purchase.ticketseller.ca/ChooseSeats/45401\">BUY June 6 at 1:30 pm</a><span><br/></span><a href=\"https://purchase.ticketseller.ca/ChooseSeats/45601\">BUY June 6 at 6:30 pm</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Get ready for another fun performance as <span class=\"BoldText\">Standing Ovation 2026</span> is back, celebrating 23 years of dance excellence in Vernon! This year's recital is bigger, bolder, and more electrifying than ever, showcasing the incredible talent, dedication, and growth of our dancers. From powerful hip hop to graceful contemporary, high energy jazz to show stopping musical theatre, every performance is designed to captivate, inspire, and leave you wanting more.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Our dancers have spent the season pushing their limits, building confidence, and bringing their artistry to life - and NOW it's their moment to shine! Whether it's your first recital or your tenth (or more!), <span class=\"BoldText\">Standing Ovation 2026</span> is a celebration of everything we love about dance: the music, the movement, the community, and the magic of the stage. Get ready to clap, cheer, and of course, give a standing ovation!
""";
