<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/77201ACHJGSDMKVSDQSJLPVNTKPPQRMCG> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Australian Bee Gees Show";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$69.00 Per Person<span><br/></span></span>Including fees & charges<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Direct from Las Vegas!</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>It's Saturday Night Fever every night with \"<span class=\"BoldText\">The Australian Bee Gees Show</span> - A Tribute to the Bee Gees\". One of the most successful and adored acts in musical history is recreated live in concert. You'll hear hits like, \"Staying Alive\", \"You Should Be Dancing,\" \"How Deep Is Your Love,\" and \"Jive Talkin.\"<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The performers' authentic take on the trio's clothes, style and moves showcase five decades of the Brothers Gibb's success as rock and disco legends, while audiences groove to their memorable music and are immersed in the disco era. The President of the Bee Gees Fan Club, USA has said, \"In my opinion they are the best Bee Gees tribute in the world!\" The Las Vegas Review Journal has named them Best Tribute Show for 2015 and again in 2019!<span><br/></span>
""";
