<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/76401ADQTCVSBMHNJBVTLKRDDQKCTSTRJ> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Cheesecake Burlesque Revue";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$49.00 Per Person (18+)</span><span><br/></span>Including fees & charges<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Celebrating 20 ridiculous years of burlesque brilliance! <span class=\"BoldText\">The Cheesecake Burlesque Revue</span> is an internationally recognized burlesque company from Victoria, BC, Canada, known for its high-energy, comedic performances, spectacular costumes, and joyful, audience-focused performances.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">The Cheesecakes</span> keep audiences coming back for more! They have dazzled and delighted in Las Vegas, New York, New Orleans, San Francisco, Seattle, Edinburgh, Helsinki, Paris, Stockholm, Rome, Bruges, and Berlin, as well as all across Canada. The Cheesecakes are passionate empowerment ambassadors and continually spread their message about body acceptance. Every body is a good body, and everybody is beautiful!!! Armed with a sassy-silliness, and a g-force of glitter, they pack a sparkly punch that will make your heart happy and leave you loving the skin you're in!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The performers are as diverse as their audience: ranging from 20S to 50S, in many shapes, sizes, and cultural backgrounds. In 2024, the company was awarded Best Large Group at the Burlesque Hall of Fame in Las Vegas, cementing its reputation for excellence, professionalism, and crowd-pleasing spectacle.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Ages 18+<span><br/></span></span><span><br/></span>
""";
