<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/69401AHRLMSBQLVDQNDHQJHGMBCGHMNBC> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Dreamboats";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$59.00 Per Person</span><span><br/></span>Including fees & taxes<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Take a trip back to the golden age of rock 'n' roll with <span class=\"BoldText\">The Dreamboats</span> - a high-energy quartet breathing new life into the sounds of the 1950s and '60s. With infectious charisma, razor-sharp musicianship, and timeless style, they’ve become one of the most exciting retro acts on today’s music scene.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Originally from Canada and now based in California, <span class=\"BoldText\">The Dreamboats</span> deliver an electrifying live show that blends vintage charm with youthful swagger. Their performances channel the spirit of <span class=\"BoldText\">Chuck Berry, Buddy Holly, Elvis Presley, and The Beatles</span>, infused with fresh, contemporary energy that gets audiences dancing, singing, and capturing every moment.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>But this is no throwback gimmick—it’s a real-deal rock 'n' roll experience. Every note is live, with all four members singing, playing, and pouring everything into the performance. Think, slick guitar moves, tight harmonies, and a stage show that’s as wild as it is tight. From behind-the-back solos and choreographed grooves to spontaneous crowd moments and dancefloor shenanigans, <span class=\"BoldText\">The Dreamboats</span> blur the line between band and audience—and make sure everyone’s part of the action.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Their journey has taken them from Canada and throughout the US to international stages, including Liverpool’s legendary Cavern Club and even a swim in Elvis Presley’s pool. They play relentlessly, committed to spreading the joy and spirit of early rock 'n' roll to new generations.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Whether you're reliving the classics or discovering them for the first time, The Dreamboats promise a night of unforgettable entertainment.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Fall in love all over again - with rock 'n' roll!<span><br/></span></span><span><br/></span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2027-03-07T19:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/ticketseller/files/1eb026bb-9fec-4fe3-b5b6-c58f40f5c328.jpg>;
