<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/64601AHJJJGRPPGBJRDJBKDBVLLBQMRLP> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Price Is Jeopardy Or No Deal Of Fortune";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">​$49 - All Seats</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">includes fees & taxes</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">'The Price Is Jeopardy Or No Deal Of Fortune'</span> brings the game show out of your TV and into your life. This fully interactive experience blends trivia, music, physical challenges, singing, luck and a whole lot of fun to get you shouting, dancing, pointing, guessing, and laughing—possibly all at once! Don't just come to see the show, come to BE the show.​<span><br/></span>
""";
