<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/42001AQJJQTSKLLKMRKNHHDRNVHRLPNPB> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Tea Party";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$79.00 All Seats</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Includes fees & surcharges</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The Tea Party, the multi-Platinum selling, multi-JUNO Award-nominated trio consisting of singer/guitarist/multi-instrumentalist Jeff Martin; bassist and multi-instrumentalist Stuart Chatwood; and drummer/percussionist Jeff Burrows, has returned fresh from their headlining Fall 2025 tour with Headstones and Finger Eleven, celebrating the 25th anniversary of their chart-topping album TRIPtych, (featuring their #1 single Heaven Coming Down).<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Since releasing their major-label debut album Splendor Solis in 1993, The Tea Party has come to be regarded as one of the world’s most innovative rock bands, with a sound that incorporates everything from traditional instrumentation from around the globe, to cutting-edge digital technology. Now, after more than 30 years as a band—and over 3million albums sold, The Tea Party is ready to open a new chapter in its saga—a story that remains rooted in the goal to create new, ambitious, and thought-provoking music.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Regarded as a progressive rock band, The Tea Party's style fuses \"blues, industrial rock, and psych-blasted progressive rock with Middle Eastern influences.\" The band has described their style as \"Moroccan-roll\". Tuonela magazine described the band's style as \"a very emotive style of alternative rock, with hints of grunge and even some touches of oriental music\".<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Not to be confused with the US political movement, The Tea Party since added the phrase \"No politics... Just Rock and Roll\" to their website.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Don’t miss Canada’s own The Tea Party, an unforgettable VDPAC Signature Concert Series experience!
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-06-30T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/ticketseller/files/12017b49-b09a-4f14-8435-e1d7d4c4680b.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/ticketseller/location/601APNNMRMBJQQPBSCNQGQHGKKCRPSSGN>;
  schema:offers _:1290a8eb9d794355b3e34223272b36865708;
  schema:duration "PT120M";
  schema:endDate "2026-06-30T21:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

