  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$48.50 Regular (until April 30th)<span><br/></span>$55.50 Last Call (May 1st)</span><span><br/></span>Includes fees & charges<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Following sold out events from coast to coast, Jokers Canada is (finally!) making its Vernon debut on Friday, May 1st. Enjoy a night with our country’s funniest comedians live from your city’s amazing theatre.Purchase online in advance to save $. More info jokerscanada.ca or @jokerscanada<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Scheduled Performers:<span><br/></span>*<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/slimtschridy?utm_source=ticketseller.ca\">Damonde Tschritter</a>: As the first Canadian to ever win the prestigious Seattle International Comedy Festival, Damonde is an icon in Canadian comedy.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>*<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/theharrisanderson?utm_source=ticketseller.ca\">Harris Anderson</a>: One of the most relatable comedic minds in our country. Often heard on Sirius XM, audiences love the amazingly talented Harris.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>*<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/aaronthecomedian?utm_source=ticketseller.ca\">Aaron Arya</a>: As featured in Just For Laughs Vancouver & Departure Festival Toronto; Aaron’s self depreciating humour makes him a fan favourite from coast to coast. + more amazing comedians!
""";
