<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/55601ASTJQNJRRQPJSDBVGNRVCPBBGHJK> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Yoga with Goats at Historic O'Keefe Ranch";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$28.75 - Admission<span><br/></span></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">includes fees & taxes</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Yoga with Goats is back for another season of fun at the Historic O'Keefe Ranch! Join Samantha Richardson and our four-legged friends through a one-hour yoga session while immersed in the beautiful nature of the ranch.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Class is 9-10am</span> (please arrive at least 5-10 minutes early to settle in) and your ticket includes admission to explore Historic O'keefe Ranch once class is over. There is zero expectation to participate in the yoga poses and no pressure to do anything that you don't want to do. The flow of class will be very gentle and encourage you to slow down and be present in your body and in the present moment. Enjoy yourself while getting to know the friendly goats and join for a few nice stretches and mindful deep breaths if you feel called to. Bring a friend and the whole family to share in the experience and don't forget a camera to capture the memories!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please bring your own yoga mat or towel. You will be out in the elements, bring everything you need to be safe and comfortable - water bottle, sunscreen, etc. No refunds. In the event of heavy rain, class will be cancelled, and your ticket will be honored at one of our future dates.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>If you have any questions, please call Historic O'keefe Ranch at 250-542-7868<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Thank you so much for your support! We look forward to sharing this unique, playful, and zen experience with you.<span><br/></span>
""";
